  m_text: 'The aim of the game is to get the highest score by shooting the Vampires,
    Skeletons, Robots and Jumping Ninjas while avoiding shooting Animals and dodging
    Cars.


    The point system is as follows:


    Robots & Ninjas = <color=#00b518>30pts</color>

    Vampire
    = <color=#00b518>25pts</color>

    Skeleton = <color=#00b518>20pts</color>

    Animals
    = <color=#da002c>-10pts</color>

